* âœ… No downloading (YouTube live stream, not download)
* âœ… No ffmpeg
* âœ… Only OpenCV (`gocv`) for video capture
* âœ… Send frames as JPEG (or raw if needed) over **UDP socket**
* âœ… Server renders MJPEG over HTTP to the browser

