```txt
Client
â”œâ”€â”€ OpenCV reads YouTube stream (via URL)
â”œâ”€â”€ Compresses frame to JPEG
â””â”€â”€ Sends via UDP â†’ Server

Server
â”œâ”€â”€ Receives UDP frames
â”œâ”€â”€ Stores latest frame
â””â”€â”€ Streams MJPEG over HTTP

Browser
â””â”€â”€ Views live stream via MJPEG
```

