## âœ… Final Setup Summary

| Component       | Role                              | Tech                  |
| --------------- | --------------------------------- | --------------------- |
| `client_udp.go` | Fetch YouTube â†’ encode â†’ UDP send | `Go + GoCV`           |
| `server_udp.go` | Receive â†’ serve MJPEG             | `Go + HTTP`           |
| Browser         | View `/stream`                    | MJPEG via `<img>` tag |

