## ðŸ§ª To Run

1. Install:

```bash
pip install yt-dlp
```

2. Run Server:

```bash
go run server_udp.go
```

3. Run Client:

```bash
go run client_udp.go
```

4. Open Browser:

```
http://localhost:8080/stream
```

